was that I heard you draw.

15:18.129 --> 15:21.129
<i>[tense music]</i>

15:21.129 --> 15:22.470
<i>♪ ♪</i>

15:22.470 --> 15:24.999
[audience laughs]

15:24.999 --> 15:28.369
So this was something, um...

15:28.369 --> 15:31.029
yes, this was something
that was a swoop,

15:31.029 --> 15:37.729
and a down something,
almost like a banana, or...

15:37.729 --> 15:41.399
a smile or something
along those lines.

15:41.399 --> 15:45.570
And there was...something...

15:45.570 --> 15:48.700
coming up from it here.
I don't think it was a banana.

15:48.700 --> 15:52.800
It was more solid than that,
but it had that sort of

15:52.800 --> 15:55.499
idea to it, and...

15:55.499 --> 15:58.570
yes, there was something
coming up from it, and...

15:58.570 --> 16:00.800
Sorry, this was--
I couldn't hear you

16:00.800 --> 16:03.470
as well as
I would have liked to.

16:03.470 --> 16:05.629
Yes.

16:05.629 --> 16:08.930
I think I know
what you've drawn.

16:08.930 --> 16:11.170
You've drawn a boat.

16:11.170 --> 16:14.300
[cheers and applause]

16:17.430 --> 16:20.869
- Rebecca Herrera!

16:20.869 --> 16:23.229
Hi.
- Hi, nice to meet you.

16:23.229 --> 16:25.899
- Nice to meet you, too.
- Ah.

16:25.899 --> 16:28.229
- That was risky,
working with Teller,

16:28.229 --> 16:30.670
because he even draws silently.
- He does.

16:30.670 --> 16:32.830
- Yeah, yeah.
- He draws very quietly.

16:32.830 --> 16:36.269
- Wow, was that nerve-wracking
picking one of them

16:36.269 --> 16:39.570
to do this with?
- Yes, it was nerve-wracking.

16:39.570 --> 16:42.129
But exciting, because it means
that they get to have

16:42.129 --> 16:44.529
a kind of close up look at me,

16:44.529 --> 16:46.300
and what's going on,
and that's what I want.

16:46.300 --> 16:48.729
I want them to have
the best chance possible.

16:48.729 --> 16:50.570
- Yes.
- To see what's going on.

16:50.570 --> 16:53.399
- So you see the shapes as
you listen to the drawing?

16:53.399 --> 16:55.269
Is that--
you're visualizing it?

16:55.269 --> 16:57.029
- Yes, so kind of like
I did with everyone

16:57.029 --> 16:59.029
where I drew the square.

16:59.029 --> 17:01.470
It's like, it was
a more kind of further version

17:01.470 --> 17:04.169
along from that, like,
you can hear when things are

17:04.169 --> 17:07.300
