and are short or long,

17:07.300 --> 17:10.770
and--or curved, and you
kind of build it together

17:10.770 --> 17:12.829
and the kind of elements in it.

17:12.829 --> 17:16.000
Sometimes it can take a while,
but once you've got it, it's--

17:16.000 --> 17:18.929
- Yeah, well, when you drew the
square, I still heard a circle.

17:18.929 --> 17:20.898
- Oh, really?
- So I'm clearly

17:20.898 --> 17:22.429
not cut out for this.

17:22.429 --> 17:25.000
Okay, it's time
to go to the boys.

17:25.000 --> 17:27.099
Penn, Teller, anything?

17:27.099 --> 17:30.669
- This was a, uh...
this was a tough one.

17:30.669 --> 17:32.100
This is a tough one, Rebecca.

17:32.100 --> 17:35.629
Really good, you know,
this is um, uh...

17:35.629 --> 17:37.570
Reading sound that's being done

17:37.570 --> 17:39.570
