17:54.969 --> 17:56.399
Teller did check your ears.

17:56.399 --> 17:58.869
He checked very, very
carefully in your ears.

17:58.869 --> 18:02.429
We think you might be
getting...uh, I don't know.

18:02.429 --> 18:04.070
We don't want to
--we--well, we--

18:04.070 --> 18:05.500
