18:05.500 --> 18:08.369
We're not allowed to go all TSA
on you and search you.

18:08.369 --> 18:10.429
[laughter]

18:10.429 --> 18:14.000
So it seems like we should...

18:14.000 --> 18:17.330
uh, we should know
how you got that information.

18:17.330 --> 18:20.570
That seems like
that's the whole trick.

18:20.570 --> 18:23.530
