18:40.469 --> 18:43.300
- Thank you so much,
thank you so much.

18:43.300 --> 18:46.270
A beautiful prize.
Thank you so much!

18:46.270 --> 18:49.530
- Whoo, Rebecca Herrera!

18:49.530 --> 18:52.869
- Yay!
- Thank you, all right!

