28:03.569 --> 28:06.430
<i>It's like, would the real
Ian Stewart please stand up?</i>

28:06.430 --> 28:07.930
Today, I'm using crossbows.

28:07.930 --> 28:09.630
<i>[heavy rock music]</i>

28:09.630 --> 28:11.269
<i>I've been doing this
a long time,</i>

28:11.269 --> 28:14.370
<i>but I am using
really dangerous objects,</i>

28:14.370 --> 28:18.900
and accidents do happen.
I could actually get hurt.

28:18.900 --> 28:22.729
Hopefully, tonight, I'll have
the nerves of steel I need

28:22.729 --> 28:24.299
<i>to pull this trick off.</i>

28:27.330 --> 28:31.069
[cheers and applause]

28:31.069 --> 28:34.930
- Please welcome
daring deceiver Ian Stewart!

28:37.969 --> 28:42.900
- Today, I brought
with me a very bad idea.

28:42.900 --> 28:44.200
[audience laughs]

28:44.200 --> 28:47.469
It all started in my garage
with a crossbow.

28:47.469 --> 28:50.400
I found a solenoid.
It's just an electric motor

28:50.400 --> 28:53.600
that pulls in
when electricity is applied.

28:53.600 --> 28:57.170
I put the solenoid on the
trigger of the crossbow,

28:57.170 --> 29:01.769
ran it to a plug,
and put a button mid-way.

29:01.769 --> 29:05.299
So that when I
press the button, hopefully,

29:05.299 --> 29:08.969
it will fire the crossbow into
that target if we're lucky.

29:11.969 --> 29:16.269
[applause]

29:16.269 --> 29:18.969
The more perceptive of you
would have noticed

29:18.969 --> 29:22.069
behind me, I've placed
four more targets,

29:22.069 --> 29:28.370
four more crossbows,
and four more firing buttons.

29:28.370 --> 29:30.370
With the first crossbow,
there was just one wire.

29:30.370 --> 29:32.100
Well, we have four this time.

29:32.100 --> 29:35.529
And generally, you would run
the wires nice and neatly,

29:35.529 --> 29:37.430
so that you could see
which crossbow

29:37.430 --> 29:40.269
was fired by which button.

29:40.269 --> 29:42.370
Today, we were
in a bit of a hurry.

29:42.370 --> 29:43.930
Unfortunately,
when the crew set it up,

29:43.930 --> 29:46.729
the wires were just
left in a jumble.

29:46.729 --> 29:49.969
Meaning that now,
you don't know

29:49.969 --> 29:53.469
