with someone else.

30:21.729 --> 30:23.930
Alyson, if you would please.

30:23.930 --> 30:26.469
[audience laughs]

30:26.469 --> 30:28.400
Have you ever
fired a crossbow before?

30:28.400 --> 30:31.069
- Not at a person.
- Not--no.

30:31.069 --> 30:34.100
Step forward, if you would,
please, to the buttons.

30:34.100 --> 30:37.029
These buttons, like I said,
each one will fire a crossbow.

